subject: Official Notice: Updates to OlyBet Terms and Conditions, Sports Rules, and Privacy Notice
bodyHtml:
Hi there,

We’ve made some important updates to our Terms and Conditions, Sports Rules, and Privacy Notice. These changes take effect immediately and apply to all users.

To continue using our services, you’ll need to review and accept the updated terms. We’ve put together a summary below to help you quickly understand what’s changed, but we strongly recommend reading the full documents.

Terms and Conditions & Sports Rules – Summary of Changes:

  1. Section 10: Customer Support and AI Usage
    A new section has been added to outline the use of artificial intelligence in customer support channels, including limitations and safeguards.
  2. Customer Responsibility – Cross-Border Gambling
    Customers located outside the Republic of Estonia are now expressly required to ensure that accessing OlyBet’s services is legal under their local laws.
  3. Payout Processing for Large Wins
    We have clarified the expected timelines and procedures for the processing of large winning payouts.
  4. Responsible Gaming Section Enhanced
    The section on responsible gaming has been amended to provide more robust guidance, support resources, and clearer descriptions of available tools.
  5. BetGames Rules Introduced
    Specific rules and clarifications have been added for BetGames, detailing how the games function and how outcomes are settled.
  6. Sports Rules – Structural and Content Updates
    • Reorganised Structure: We’ve restructured the Sports Rules to better match your journey — from placing a bet to seeing it settled.
    • New Sports Added: Rules for newly offered sports have been introduced.
    • Clarifications for Existing Sports: Existing rules have been updated to provide clearer guidance on how markets function and are settled.
    • New Market Types: Additional market types have been introduced with full explanations of how they operate and are settled.
    • Esports Section Revamped: A comprehensive update including new titles, market types, and settlement rules.
    • Bet Builder Section Added: New rules outlining how Bet Builder bets are formed and settled.
    • Extraordinary Circumstances: We have provided more comprehensive explanations on how bets are settled in extraordinary scenarios, such as event cancellations, player withdrawals, or changes to competition formats.

Privacy Notice – Summary of Changes:

  1. Updated to Reflect Revised Processing Activities
    The Privacy Notice now reflects recent changes in how personal data is collected, used, and stored.
  2. General Improvements
    Language and structure have been refined to make the notice clearer, more transparent, and easier to understand.

For any questions, please contact our Customer Support team.

OlyBet - Everything is possible!
